summary: Simply adds a Mp focused player home with a wip puzzle to enter it.
descriptionHtml:
[center]
This is a ALPHA version of a multiplayer house (Yes MP this mod is going to act as a side modfor the yet to be released Skyrim Together Mod) This is also myFIRST mod so please be nice :) My aim of this modis to make a home where more than one player can live.

Currently it contains the man room and exterior

The [b][u]Forge room[/u][/b] is currently in progress I am looking forsome people who are ok at room building each person can make a separate room
if you want to make a room please contact me VIA discord 

If you are reporting a bug or got a suggestion DM me on discord much easier that way for me to talk to you guys :)[b][/b][u][/u][color=#0066cc][/color]
[u][i][b][size=6]DISCORD[/size][/b][/i][/u] - [url=https://discord.gg/suMZfs][u][color=#0066cc][size=6]https://discord.gg/suMZfs[/size][/color][/u][/url]
Credit to RonnieMagnum for the textures and to this guy https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16446[/center]
